            <a href="/opinion/opinion/2015855/youth-inclusion-a-must-in-governing"><img src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/newdesign/assets/images/bg/default-pic-w600.jpg" class="img-fluid lazy" data-src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201108/c1_2015855_201108050533.jpg" title="Youth inclusion a must in governing" alt="Youth inclusion a must in governing" data-srcset="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201108/c1_2015855_201108050533_126.jpg 350w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201108/c1_2015855_201108050533_216.jpg 500w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201108/c1_2015855_201108050533_216.jpg 700w"></a>
