            <h3><a href="/opinion/opinion/2015983/the-milkman-who-became-a-secret-agent">The milkman who became a secret agent</a> </h3> 
            <p>To briefly escape from the US election mayhem, an appreciation of actor Sean Connery who died last week aged 90, seems to be in order. I had somehow thought Connery would go on forever, just like the Bond films. It is an intriguing tale of an Edinburgh milkman who became the most famous fictional spy in the world.</p> 
            <div class="f-icon"> <span class="fa-date-showmobi">8 Nov 2020 </span> <!-- show mobile --> <span class="ic-comment"><a href="/opinion/opinion/2015983/the-milkman-who-became-a-secret-agent?view_comment=1"><i class="icon-comment"></i> 6</a></span> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="listnews-row "> 
          <div class="listnews-col-left"> 
           <div class="listnews-datetime">
