              <img src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/newdesign/assets/images/bg/default-pic-w600.jpg" class="lazy" data-src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936.jpg" alt="Target the PM2.5 source" title="Target the PM2.5 source" data-srcset="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_32.jpg 350w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_32.jpg 500w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_32.jpg 700w">
             </div> 
             <div class="columnnist-name">
              BY <a href="/opinion/columnist/936" class="link-unterline">Editorial</a>
