            <h3><a href="/opinion/opinion/2015615/target-the-pm2-5-source">Target the PM2.5 source</a> </h3> 
            <p>December is known for being the beginning of the PM2.5 season in Bangkok and several other provinces.</p> 
            <div class="f-icon"> <span class="fa-date-showmobi">7 Nov 2020 </span> <!-- show mobile --> <span class="ic-comment"><a href="/opinion/opinion/2015615/target-the-pm2-5-source?view_comment=1"><i class="icon-comment"></i> 15</a></span> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
           <div class="listnews-img">
            <a href="/opinion/opinion/2015615/target-the-pm2-5-source"><img src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/newdesign/assets/images/bg/default-pic-w600.jpg" class="img-fluid lazy" data-src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201107/c1_2015615_201107051706.jpg" title="Target the PM2.5 source" alt="Target the PM2.5 source" data-srcset="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201107/c1_2015615_201107051706_126.jpg 350w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201107/c1_2015615_201107051706_216.jpg 500w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20201107/c1_2015615_201107051706_216.jpg 700w"></a>
